OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC Two's Newsnight is to be cut back  
OL,6, and have its format overhauled as part 
OL,7, of a plan to save money in the         
OL,8, corporation's news department.         
OL,10,FThe long-running show will lose its    
OL,11,Fdedicated reporters, be shortened by 10
OL,12,Fminutes and drop its investigative     
OL,13,Ffilms to focus on studio-based debates.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, the BBC News at One TV      
OL,16,Fbulletin will be extended to an hour   
OL,17,Fand will be broadcast from Salford.    
OL,19,FThe BBC also said it would put more    
OL,20,Fmoney into digital journalism.         
